dininginfo.name: Canyon Vista
dininginfo.description: Dine on a breezy outdoor terrace overlooking the canyon, or next to a roaring fireplace. Canyon Vista’s menu includes pizza, pasta, Mediterranean favorites, Asian cuisine, made-to-order sandwiches and a variety of hot grilled items.
dininginfo.pageDescription: Dine on a breezy outdoor terrace overlooking the canyon, or next to a roaring fireplace. Canyon Vista’s menu includes pizza, pasta, Mediterranean favorites, Asian cuisine, made-to-order sandwiches and a variety of hot grilled items.
